    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Ready to Build Something Amazing?</h2>
            <p>Join thousands of developers using GeForce APIs to power their projects.</p>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-user-plus mr-2"></i> Create Your Free Account Now</a>
